snippet.title: Warlock's Tower - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Warlock's Tower is a punishing puzzler in a GameBoy aesthetic with elegantly designed levels around one brutal rule - one move equals one life lost
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/warlocks-tower/id1111603555
Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.midipixel.warlockstower
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/530370/
